    "In parallel, reduced DCT coefficients obtained from the three CNNs are concatenated and then a feature selection approach is used to select significant features.",
    "Lastly, individual and ensemble classifiers are employed to classify CRC images.",
    "The summary of Color-CADx steps is given in Fig. 3.",
    "Initially, the aspects of the CRC images of both datasets are changed to be equivalent to the input length of each CNN.",
    "For ResNet50 and DenseNet201 they are modified to 224 × 224 × 3, whereas for AlexNet they are changed to 227 × 227 × 3."
